ChangeToken.description: The value returned by the most recent call to GetChangeToken.

IPSetId.description: The IPSetId of the IPSet that you want to update. IPSetId is returned by CreateIPSet and by ListIPSets.

Updates.description: An array of IPSetUpdate objects that you want to insert into or delete from an IPSet. For more information, see the applicable data types:    IPSetUpdate: Contains Action and IPSetDescriptor     IPSetDescriptor: Contains Type and Value
